发一款适配微信小游戏平台的中国象棋游戏，支持玩家进行：\n- 人机对战\n- 本地双人对战\n- 在线匹配对战（可选）\n- 复盘、悔棋、提示等辅助功能\n\n目标是实现：\n- 轻量、快速加载\n- 操作简单、界面清晰\n- 规则准确、下棋体验流畅\n- 适配微信小游戏运行环境\n\n### 1.3 目标用户\n- 象棋爱好者\n- 休闲玩家\n- 微信小游戏用户\n- 想利用碎片时间下棋的用户\n\n---\n\n## 2. 产品定位\n\n### 2.1 核心定位\n一款“轻量、即开即玩、规则标准”的中国象棋小游戏。\n\n### 2.2 核心卖点\n- 无需下载安装，微信内直接打开\n- 3 秒内进入游戏\n- 支持单局快速对战\n- AI 难度可调\n- 支持悔棋、提示、认输\n- 适合好友娱乐和休闲消遣\n\n---\n\n## 3. 功能需求\n\n## 3.1 基础功能\n\n### 3.1...\n\n<read-files>\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/README.md\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/package.json\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/.openclaw/workspace-state.json\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/AGENTS.md\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/MEMORY.md\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/SOUL.md\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/USER.md\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-03-20.md\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-03-21.md\n</read-files>\n\n<workspace-critical-rules>\n## Every Session\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Safety\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>","firstKeptEntryId":"35c2a443","tokensBefore":105741,"details":{"readFiles":["/home/gem/workspace/agent/README.md","/home/gem/workspace/agent/package.json","/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/.openclaw/workspace-state.json","/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/AGENTS.md","/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/MEMORY.md","/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/SOUL.md","/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/USER.md","/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-03-20.md","/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-03-21.md"],"modifiedFile